          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是如此，老管家你就收拾去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（华忠下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "安学海",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人浓墨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "安学海",
          "line_type": "二黄顶板",
          "musical_style": "二黄顶板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老华忠可算得忠义大，\n远途辛苦还要亏他。\n字谕我儿悉根芽：\n黄河水涨漫无涯。\n索银六千将父罚。\n变卖银两交与管家。\n快唤华忠付托他。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（华忠背包自下场门上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "收拾包裹身背定，\n老奴就此要登程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "安学海",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我今付你这书信，\n劳你年迈受劳辛。\n见了我儿详细云。"
        },
        {
          "character": "一路之上须谨慎、华忠",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷不必细叮咛，\n我受厚恩当尽心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（华忠走。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "安学海",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管家转来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤回老奴为何因？"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷有何吩咐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "安学海",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，管家呀！此番进京变卖房产，须要及早回来；若是迟误，恐怕你老爷要\n吃苦了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷请把心放定，\n老奴星夜赶途程。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（华忠下。安学海望，哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "安学海",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "华忠，管家呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "安学海",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "华忠上路泪难忍，\n不由下官挂在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "但愿早来事安稳、佟夫人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且免愁烦听好音。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（安学海、佟夫人同下。）"
        }
      ],
