    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（褚一官上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了岳父命，四路谢宾朋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，褚一官。奉了岳父之命，四路拜谢亲友。俱已谢毕，回庄便了。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侠义门前三千事，待客还须半子劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（褚一官下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "念": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "华忠",
        "褚一官"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（华忠上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "早行晚宿奔途程，\n盘费用尽无计行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉行了旬日，银钱用尽，这便怎么处？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（华忠望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看那边来了一人，好像我那妹丈褚一官，待我向前看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。褚一官上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可是我妹丈？"
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是舅兄。久违了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹丈一向可好，为何到此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舅兄有所不知，你我离别日久，不幸你令妹亡故，因为相隔路远，一时难与舅\n兄送信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我妹亡故了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀。贤妹呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（华忠哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，妹丈，你在此作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舅兄不知。此处有廿八棵红柳村，有一邓九公，将我招赘为婿。今日幸会舅兄，\n请到庄上盘桓几日。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有要事在身，还要赶路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事如此紧急？"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因黄河决口，总槽将我老爷参奏，罚银六千两，我家老爷为官清正，不取民\n财，任所没有许多银两，命我进京变卖房产，方可赎罪，故而要急急赶路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既有要事，不敢强留，改日再会。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（褚一官、华忠分走。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，妹丈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "舅兄？"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我盘费用尽，你有现成银两，请借我使用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这有散碎银两，不知够用否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "华忠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "足以够用，我就去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（华忠下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "褚一官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺回庄便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（褚一官下。）"
        }
      ],
